# Performance gates keep a small checked-in D3D11 baseline set. Ignore
# machine-specific runs unless they are deliberately force-added.
Saved/PerformanceReports/**
!Saved/PerformanceReports/cold-start-d3d11.json
!Saved/PerformanceReports/resource-stress-d3d11.json
!Saved/PerformanceReports/scene-transition-d3d11.json
!Saved/PerformanceReports/warm-gameplay-d3d11.json

